title: Loafer
subTitle: Seenu, a man who wants to go to Dubai, meets and falls in love with Madhumati. When he discovers that a dreaded don has killed his friend and Madhumati's brother, he sets out to exact revenge.

title: Super Ranga
subTitle: Ranga, a reckless thrill-seeker, falls in love with Swathi who makes him promise to be more responsible. However, she breaks up with him when he goes back to his old ways.

title: Bunglow No 17
subTitle: Gautham and Deeksha, along with their daughter, move into an isolated bungalow gifted to them by Gautham's father. Soon, they start experiencing paranormal activities around the house.

title: 777 Charlie
subTitle: Dharma, a broken man drowning in despair, finds his world transformed when he rescues Charlie, an abused pup. Later, they embark on a journey of hope and redemption.

title: Etharkkum Thunindhavan
subTitle: Kannabiran, a lawyer, saves a young woman from a pornography racket run by Inba, a minister's son. However, Inba threatens to leak explicit videos of several women, making Kannabiran go after him.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Darbar
subTitle: Aaditya, a high-ranking law enforcement official, sets out to eradicate the city's gangsters. As the events unfold, it becomes clear that his motivations are deeply personal.

title: Main hoon Surya Singham 2
subTitle: An undercover police officer works in a school and tries to put an end to the criminal activities of two criminals who rule the area.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jihadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jihadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: George Reddy
subTitle: George Reddy, a student leader in Osmania University, decides to revolt against the injustice and economic inequalities in society.

title: War On Terror Kandahar
subTitle: After a group of terrorists hijack a plane, an army major and the National Security Guard set off against all odds on a rescue mission.

title: Vasco The Rebel
subTitle: With unwavering support from his lover, a defiant young man carves his way into the mafia world. His journey takes a turn when a relentless police officer pursues him.

title: Ram Ki Jung
subTitle: Ram does not believe in everlasting love and this ideology does not go down well with Jaanu. When Abhishek, a police officer, asks him the reason, he tells him about Rooba, his former lover.

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Angel
subTitle: Nani discovers a rare antique idol from the excavation site at Amaravati. He wants to sell it and keep the money for himself, but before he can do that, the idol goes missing.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi
subTitle: A man and a woman develop a great bond after the latter arrives in Hyderabad. However, they realise their love for each other when the woman's marriage is arranged to a person of her parent's choice.

title: Yudh Ek Jung
subTitle: Chandu, a supermarket employee, encounters trouble when he decides to help Indu, an aspiring actress, and gets embroiled in a murder case.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

title: Ragada
subTitle: Satya, a money-minded man, arrives in Hyderabad and starts working for a gangster, GK. However, he soon becomes the target of another gangster, Peddanna.

title: The Strong Man Badal
subTitle: Madhu falls in love with Ramu, a boy from her college. However, her mother insults him and has intentions of killing him.

title: The Strong Man Badal
subTitle: Madhu falls in love with Ramu, a boy from her college. However, her mother insults him and has intentions of killing him.

title: Kaapa
subTitle: When Anand finds his pregnant wife's name on Kerala's anti-social list alongside other criminals, he sets on a determined mission to clear her name and prove her innocence.

title: Aaj Ka Naya Khiladi
subTitle: Siva unknowingly crosses a ruthless gangster while robbing the Home Minister's residence. Subsequently, the gangster kidnaps the Minister's daughter in retribution.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: Dhruva
subTitle: A committed police officer, Dhruva, uncovers a web of organised crime headed by a scientist, Siddharth Abhimanyu. But when Dhruva tries to build a case against him, he faces many challenges.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: An NRI medical student falls in love with a vivacious woman. However, they face challenges in their relationship due to their differences in personalities.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi 2
subTitle: Balu grows up without the love of a family due to his parents' untimely death. Later, he decides to establish a firm to help people like himself receive the affection they missed out on.

title: Power Unlimited
subTitle: The home minister asks Tirupathi to impersonate the deceased ACP Baldev, his lookalike, to catch Ganguly, a dreaded gangster. After taking over his new role, he finds many startling revelations.

title: Rajini The Jailer
subTitle: A retired jailer lives a peaceful life with his family. But when his son, who is a policeman, goes missing and is supposedly killed, he is forced to go back to his world of crime and find the killer.

title: Dangerous Khiladi 2
subTitle: A corrupt minister's daughter finds a diary containing details about a couple's relationship. When the story ends abruptly, she sets out to find the person who wrote it.

title: Dum Man Of Power
subTitle: Tarak comes to India after his parents die in an accident and falls in love with Meera, who seeks others' happiness before hers. Soon, Tarak and Meera's relationship goes through a rough patch.
